page.title: 01GENERAL REVIEW
page.content: This area can be divided into two distinct sections. The northern part, above the motorway is mostly given over to arable{farming}whilst the area to the south is mainly given over to {industry}and residential{housing. The{population}density is far greater in the southerly part of the area, and there is intense housing development of both traditional and timber-framed types eating into the remaining agricultural land that is left. To the west of the area is a large car factory and an international airport serving the Southampton area.
